{"type":"message","id":"fd6e7ff0","parentId":"3e71c057","timestamp":"2026-03-30T08:31:17.712Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me understand the task. This is a cron job that's running the follow-builders skill. According to the instructions, I need to:\n\n1. Execute prepare-digest.js\n2. Remix the content into a digest following the prompts\n3. Deliver via deliver.js\n\nThe instructions also say \"Return your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically.\"\n\nSince this is a cron job in OpenClaw (the runtime says `channel=qqbot`), I should follow the Content Delivery workflow steps.\n\nLet me start by following the steps:\n\nStep 1: Load Config - I need to read `~/.follow-builders/config.json`\nStep 2: Run prepare-digest.js\nStep 3: Check for content\nStep 4: Remix content\nStep 5: Apply language\nStep 6: Deliver\n\nBut since this is running as a cron and says \"Return your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically\", I think I should just produce the digest and it will be sent automatically.\n\nLet me start by running the prepare-digest.js script.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"I'll execute the follow-builders digest workflow. Let me start by running the prepare script."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_27b8d85230104618877d6843","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/skills/follow-builders/scripts && node prepare-digest.js 2>/dev/null","timeout":120000}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":4769,"output":501,"cacheRead":13360,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18630,"cost":{"input":0.0028614,"output":0.0011022,"cacheRead":0.0014696000000000002,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005433200000000001}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774859455609}}
